               SCHAEFFER

               Turning, starting very slowly toward the barn.

               INT. BARN  DAY

               McElroy at the top of the ladder, looking down. Then easing 
               over, placing his feet on the rungs.

               BOOK

               He stands below in a cowpen, using the cows for cover. The 
